title: Push up extraction success rate (currently 86.4%)
description: 732/5370 URLs (13.6%) still fail extraction. The HTML fallback (PR #264) helped but several sites still have low/zero success rates: bakingbites.com (0/12), halfbakedharvest.com (0/7), feastingathome.com (0/5), kingarthurbaking.com (5/24), hostthetoast.com (3/9). This is a tracker for the overall extraction rate goal. Individual site-specific issues exist separately.
